{"id":"raisins","term":"Raisins","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Dried grapes; mentioned <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Samuel 25:18\">1 Sam. 25:18</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Samuel 30:12\">30:12</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 16:1\">2 Sam. 16:1</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 12:40\">1 Chr. 12:40</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Samuel 25:18","1 Samuel 30:12","2 Samuel 16:1","1 Chronicles 12:40"]}